        <title>使用 Github Actions 自动部署 Hugo 到仓库和服务器</title>
        <link>https://xlglife.github.io/posts/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-github-actions-%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2-hugo-%E5%88%B0%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93%E5%92%8C%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8/</link>
